causelay
========

Contents
--------
* Git versions of packages.
* Fresh ebuilds waiting for addition to the official portage tree.
* Packages that don't fit to the official portage tree.

Install
-------
layman:
layman -a causelay

manual:
git clone https://github.com/causes-/causelay
echo 'PORTDIR_OVERLAY="/home/username/causelay"' >> /etc/portage/make.conf
